metadata.description:
In celebration of @BillyM2k reaching 300K followers on Twitter, we are proud to present this one-of-one Dogecoin collectible NFT designed by @DogecoinMilitia and @DogeDrip

With this collectible coin, we are following the mission to #DoOnlyGoodEveryday!

50% of the proceeds are being donated to the American Cancer Society

Additionally, with the 1/1 NFT digital collectible, you will also receive the only minted 1/1 physical coin to match your digital asset!

Let's continue to have fun while we #DoOnlyGoodEveryday.

Cheers #ToTheMoon :)
